The Last Assault
Now that the Canian army is strong enough, an opportunity has arisen to restore order to the world once and for all. To do this you must defeat Firez's army and take over his castle.
#subobj 1
Destroy the undead army
Firez has turned the entire population of the city into undead and put them into battle. Firez's army must be defeated!
#subobj 2
Get to the palace tower
Firez has taken cover in the tower of his palace! There are still many enemies left in the city, getting further may prove difficult.